{"tid":1030941,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Fate/ Stay Night(Heaven's Feel- Lost Butterfly)","createTime":"2019-02-21T10:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T04:14:53.000Z","uid":201662,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"617a0f4be89a2e15e1ec73e441a7cd64fb5240c6","tid":1030941,"uid":201662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:18:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aj8U0iA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAj8U0iA.jpg&h=db6c580f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">故事</span><br />\n將改編遊戲《Fate/stay night》中的「Heaven's Feel」間桐櫻路線。「Heaven's Feel」有著和前兩條線截然不同的黑暗基調，以衛宮士郎在弓道部與學妹間桐櫻作為感情主線，講述間桐櫻和衛宮士郎之間的故事，並將整個聖杯戰爭的真實全貌給展露出來。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">欣賞門檻</span><br />\n最少睇過Unlimited Blade Works同 Heaven&rsquo;s Feel 第一集。若曾玩過Fate Stay Night則體驗感覺更佳。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上映時間</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmovie6.com/movie/48898#showtimes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmovie6.com%2Fmovie%2F48898%23showtimes&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFeaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=ee0e8cec\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkmovie6.com/movie/48898#showtimes</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">配音</span> <br />\n衛宮士郎：杉山紀彰<br />\nSaber：川澄綾子<br />\n間桐櫻：下屋則子<br />\nRider：淺川悠<br />\n遠坂凜：植田佳奈<br />\nArcher：諏訪部順一<br />\n伊莉雅絲菲爾&middot;馮&middot;愛因茲貝倫：門脇舞以<br />\nBerserker：西前忠久<br />\n間桐慎二：神谷浩史<br />\n間桐臓硯：津嘉山正種<br />\n真Assassin：稲田徹<br />\n言峰綺禮：中田譲治<br />\n吉爾伽美什：關智一<br />\n藤村大河：伊藤美紀<br />\n衛宮切嗣：小山力也<br />\n<br />\n若已入場欣賞過，歡迎到下方討論。"},{"pid":"cb2fa55a38eee8a24af02194e157e73c99cbe0cf","tid":1030941,"uid":12013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"香港人一邊睇一邊有好多反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset